===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{symptom}} A [[sudden]], usually [[noisy]] [[expulsion]] of [[air]] from the [[lungs]], often [[involuntary]].
#:''Behind me, I heard a distinct, dry '''cough'''.''
